  <description>
    <p>LibrePCB is a free electronic design automation (EDA) software for developing printed circuit boards (PCBs).</p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Cross-platform (Unix/Linux, macOS, Windows)</li>
      <li>All-in-one package (project management, library/schematic/board editors)</li>
      <li>Intuitive, modern and easy-to-use graphical user interface</li>
      <li>Very powerful library design with some innovative concepts</li>
      <li>Human-readable file formats</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

